											<p class="fs-20 lh-28 fw-medium">At Intuitive Care Home Health & Hospice, our mission has always been clear — to provide care that is not only clinically exceptional, but deeply human. Every family we serve is entrusted to us during vulnerable and meaningful moments in life, and we honor that trust with unwavering dedication.</p>
											<p>Healthcare is more than a service. It is a responsibility. It is presence. It is dignity preserved in every interaction. As President, I am proud to lead a team that understands this distinction and lives it daily.</p>
