										<h2 class="fw-semibold fs-40 lh-50 text-dark-gray">A Message from Our President</h2>
										<p class="fs-20 lh-28 fw-normal text-dark-gray">Intuitive Care was founded on the belief that patients deserve more than treatment — they deserve understanding, respect, and individualized attention. Our approach to home health and hospice care reflects this commitment in every visit, every plan of care, and every conversation.</p>
										<p>We invest in highly skilled clinicians, evidence-based practices, and continuous training to ensure the highest standard of care. At the same time, we remain grounded in empathy — recognizing that behind every diagnosis is a person, a family, and a story.</p>
										<p>As healthcare continues to evolve, we remain steadfast in our principles: clinical excellence, operational integrity, and compassionate service. We do not compromise on quality. We do not waver in accountability. And we never lose sight of the human side of care.</p>
									</div>
